USUZIDLULISELE esikhungweni esizimele izicubu okholwa ukuthi ezelungu lawo ukuze kuhlolwe ulibofuzo, umndeni womfundi isidumbu sakhe okuthiwa satholwa emva kwamasonto amabili sesonakele, kulandela ukuthi emuke kuhlasela izikhukhula ngo-Ephreli. Umndeni kaLusapho Mhlongo (17), uvale ngengidi amasango esikhungo samakhaza  ePhoenix izinsuku ezimbili kusuka ngoLwesibili ufuna kukhululwe isidumbu salo mfundi obefunda eDabeka High, eNanda. Kuthiwa wamuka nomfula owawudla izindwani ngesikhathi ephuma esikoleni ezama ukuwela, watholwa emva kwamasonto amabili. Umndeni wakhe uthi  isidumbu sakhe kuthiwa sesiduve emakhazeni amasonto amahlanu kulindwe imiphumela yolibofuzo okuyinto ecasule kakhulu njengoba ukhala ngokuthi ufuna ukungcwaba. Uninomncane kamufi uNksz Dumsile Mhlongo, uthe ngoLwesithathu ngesikhathi bevale amasango, bagcine bevunyelwe ukuthi bathathe izicubu ziyohlolwa esikhungweni esizimele. “Ekuqaleni sike sakuphakamisa ukuthi sizithathe siyozihlolela thina, kodwa kwanqatshwa ngoba kuthiwa odokotela bayathengeka. Bagcine sebesivumela ukuthi amaphoyisa azithathe azihambise e-Lancet Laboratory eGateway, bathi imiphumela bazoyidedela emasontweni amane,” usho kanje. Uthe yize kunjalo, bathenjiswe emakhazeni ukuthi imiphumela izobe isikhona ngoLwesihlanu (izolo), ngakho sebelinde imiphumela ezofika kuqala, bathathe isidumbu selungu labo bayosifihla ngesizotha.  Uqinisekise ukuthi ngoLwesihlanu (izolo) bazoqhubeka nokuqhinqa emasangweni bafake ingcindezi kuze kukhululwe isidumbu. 